  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Cut your<strong> potatoes </strong>(skins on) into wedges</p><p>Add the <strong>wedges</strong> to a baking tray with <strong>half</strong> your<strong> ground smoked paprika </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp – these are your <strong>paprika wedges</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
